                "image": {
                    "type": "image",
                    "name": "Additional Lore",
                    "image": "Sidebar_2_AdditionalLore.png"
                },
                "html": "\u201cA lizard with an apple-sized gem sticking out of its forehead? Wishful thinking!\u201d<br/><br/> \u201cCarbuncles are real! I almost caught one, but even though it could barely walk, its magic allowed it to escape my clutches.\u201d<br/><br/> \u201cTheir mind control powers could make them useful familiars, but if you ever catch one, it dies of fright.\u201d<br/><br/> \u201cMy advice is to stay away from these pests. They drink your hopes and aspirations through their horns, leaving you empty except for bad luck and bellyaches.\u201d<br/><br/> \u201cPlanning a carbuncle hunt? You'd better leave your self-respect at home, and be ready to emerge with fewer friends than you had at the start!\u201d"
            }
        ],
